nodes.text: Wedding of Ghes Orade and Mirta Gev

The Wedding of Ghes Orade and Mirta Gev was the private Mandalorian wedding of Ghes Orade and Mirta Gev in Keldabe on Mandalore. While no one attended the wedding but Ghes and Mirta, several Mandalorians and non-Mandalorians attended the celebratory party afterwards.
